import React,{useState} from "react"; import axiosInstance from "./AxiosInstance"; import SidebarLayout from "./SidebarLayout"; import { Container, Box, FormControl, InputLabel, Select, MenuItem, Button, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Pagination, Dialog, DialogActions, DialogContent, DialogContentText, DialogTitle, TextField, Snackbar, Alert } from '@mui/material'; const Instructors=()=>{ return ( Time Zone State Instructor Id Address TimeZone State Instructor City CancellationPolicy PaymentMode NonrefundableFee FobKey Deposit MembershipFee UsageFee RefundableStatus BookMethod RegistrationLink {currentItems.map((venue) => ( {venue.id} {venue.address} {venue.timeZone} {venue.state} {venue.instructor} {venue.city} {venue.cancellationPolicy} {venue.paymentMode} {venue.nonrefundableFee} {venue.fobKey} {venue.deposit} {venue.membershipFee} {venue.usageFee} {venue.refundableStatus} {venue.bookMethod} {venue.registrationLink} ))}
{isEditMode?"Edit Venue":"Add a Venue"} {isEditMode?"Edit the information of the venue.":"Add the information of the venue"} Time Zone {isEditMode&&} {snackbarMessage} ); }; export default Instructors;
